pesticide.PPE: Long-sleeved shirt and long pants; Waterproof gloves; Shoes plus socks; NIOSH-approved particulate respirator with N, P or R filter with NIOSH approval number prefix TC-84A or a NIOSH-approved powered air purifying respirator with a HE filter with NIOSH approval number prefix TC-21C.

Active_Ingredients.name: Bacillus amyloliquefaciens MBI 600 (antecedent Bacillus subtilis MBI 600)

Safety_Information.general_Info: Have the product container or label with you when calling a poison control center or doctor or going for treatment. You may also contact BASF Corporation for emergency medical treatment information at 1-800-832-HELP (4357).
